; Native MongoDB backend: a Fennec_data.Backend.S over the statically-linked libmongoc driver, so the
; whole reactive / DDP / realtime stack runs over a real mongod UNCHANGED (same seam Minimongo
; implements in memory). Every blocking driver call runs in an Eio systhread so the scheduler keeps
; going. Native only (it links the C FFI + Eio) — the browser/SSR use fennec.data with the in-memory
; backend instead.
(library
 (name fennec_data_mongo)
 (public_name fennec.data.mongo)
 (libraries fennec.data fennec-mongo.ffi fennec-mongo.bson_json fennec-mongo.bson fennec-mongo.query
   eio eio.unix))
